casebody.data:
DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA, et al., petitioners,
v.
Theodore WESBY, et al. No. 15-1485. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 19, 2017.

Motion of International Municipal Lawyers Association, Inc. for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit granted.
